Privacy Policy
Welcome to Roku Remote (hereinafter referred to as "this application"). We take your privacy very seriously and are committed to protecting the security of your personal information. By using this application, you agree to the terms described in this privacy policy.
1. Information we collect
We may collect the following types of personal information:
Device information: This application may collect the model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers (such as IMEI number, advertising ID, etc.) of the device.
Usage data: We collect statistical information related to the use of the application, such as user access frequency, operation time, and function usage.
Advertising and analysis data: This application integrates advertising and Firebase analysis services, and may collect your behavioral data to improve advertising effects and application performance.
2. About children's privacy
We strictly abide by the laws and regulations on children's privacy protection. This application does not collect personal information for children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and find that your child has provided personal information, please contact us immediately. We will take necessary measures to delete this information.
3. Advertising services
This application uses third-party advertising services to provide you with advertisements. Advertisers may collect your device information and usage data to show you personalized advertising content. We integrate with the following advertising platforms:
Google AdMob: Ad service providers collect device information (such as advertising ID) to display personalized ads to you. You can choose to disable ad personalization through your device settings.
Other advertising platforms: May include other third-party advertisers to provide ads relevant to your interests.
4. Firebase
This app uses Firebase analytics services to help us understand how users use the app, analyze user behavior, and improve the performance and user experience of the app. Firebase may collect the following types of data:
Device information
Usage and behavior data
Error reports
Firebase's data collection and privacy policy follow Google's privacy policy.
5. Use of data
The information we collect will be used for the following purposes:
Provide and maintain the functionality of this app
Improve user experience
Display personalized ads to you
Perform app analysis and bug fixes
Other purposes in accordance with legal requirements
6. Data security
We are committed to protecting your personal information and taking reasonable security measures to prevent data loss, unauthorized access or tampering. However, due to the nature of the Internet, absolute security cannot be guaranteed.
7. Your rights
Under applicable data protection laws, you have the right to:
Request access to your personal data
Request correction or deletion of your personal data
Withdraw consent and stop data processing
If you have any requests or questions about your personal data, please contact us through the following contact information.
8. Contact information
If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, or need to contact us, please contact us through the following information:
Email: figuredin@gmail.com
9. Updates to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post the updated Privacy Policy on this page. Please check this Privacy Policy regularly to be aware of any changes.
